dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.enterprise.risk.sec.vuln.scordef.CompositeSecVulScoringMetricDefn
dataStructure.description:
A type of SecurityVulnerabilityMetricDefn that is formed by aggregating other SecurityVulnerabilityMetricDefns, which may be Composite or Atomic SecurityVulnerabilityMetricDefns. Notes: A Base Score Metric which is made up of Base Exploitability and Base Impact, Base Exploitability made up of Acess Vector, Authentication, and so forth.

This entity is optional
